Parameters.Parameter: Data providers, UW-Macrostrat, John J Czaplewski <john@czaplewski.org>

Datasource.Parameter: (SELECT z.map_id, COALESCE(l.color, '#777777') AS color, z.geom FROM carto_new.tiny z LEFT JOIN maps.map_legend ON z.map_id = map_legend.map_id LEFT JOIN maps.legend AS l ON l.legend_id = map_legend.legend_id) subset
(SELECT x.line_id, x.geom, q.direction, q.type FROM carto_new.lines_tiny x LEFT JOIN ( SELECT * FROM lines.tiny ) q on q.line_id = x.line_id ) subset
